Description: Picture this tranquil 25-acre gated-community landscaped with manicured greenery, mature trees and meandering pathways. These neo-traditional architecturally-designed Villa apartments have personal attached garages rich in ambiance. Each building has been carefully placed to overlook panoramas of green space. Luxury, no problem. Privacy, no problem. When you feel like slipping out for recreation, walk to your private "Country Club on the Green". Listen to the sound of the pool water over the infinity edge while you cozy up by the outside fireplace, or you can warm-up inside the Great Room while you challenge a friend to a game of billiards. Print your documents in the cyber cafe while you enjoy a freshly brewed cup of coffee. At the Club, all of your senses are stimulated!

Description: As you drive through this gated community, you will be impressed with smart, sophisticated architecture that wraps around unrivaled community amenities; all under one roof! Step inside the beautifully designed 4-story mid-rise elevator building and witness the excitement of our two story, 12,000 square foot club house, "The Hub Club", with floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking the sparkling swimming pool and recreational enclave. Our full-time concierge will greet you each day as you stop by to use free WiFi in the business center, work out in the expansive fitness center, or kick back and relax in the library. Enjoy a movie or sports event in the theater with state-of-the-art surround sound. Challenge your rival to a game of billiards or meet new friends at the cooking classes in the large Demonstration Kitchen. The Great Room extends your floor plan as you hear the grand piano and see the glow of the fireplace. "People meeting People", that's Serenity Place at Dorsey Ridge.

Description: There are many great aspects to living at The Elms at Stoney Run Village. For starters, we are located in an excellent neighborhood full of world-class shopping, entertainment, and transportation options. One of the first aspects you will notice is that we are located right across the street from Arundel Mills Mall. Inside this shopping paradise, you can find Cinemark Theaters, a 24 screen movie theater as well as a host of stores, including Best Buy, Saks Fifth Avenue off 5th and Old Navy. Check out the mall directory to see additional stores. The mall also has several restaurants, including Johnny Rockets, Buffalo Wild Wings, and much more. This same center is also home to Maryland Live Casino. Here you can find a full-service casino, delicious dining options such as The Cheesecake Factory, Bobby's Burger Palace, The Prime Rib, Md Live Buffet as well as RamsHead Center Stage, a state-of-the-art performance venue. Description: A mid-rise and garden-style community with the finest amenities, a posh pool and clubhouse, and award-winning resident services ? that's what's on offer in these Baltimore-area apartments. Arbors at ArundelPreserve boasts spacious floor plans with upscale details like maple cabinetry, granite countertops and even gas fireplaces in select suites. Better yet, it's all just a stone's throw from Baltimore and D.C. Outside your beautiful apartment home, enjoy a stroll through the tree-lined neighborhood to pick up a pastry or bottle of wine, or take a woodsy walk with your pup. (No weight restrictions on pets here!) Thanks to the thoughtful design of this tucked-away oasis, you'd never guess the chic shopping of Arundel Mills is just a mile way. And who knew commuting could be such a breeze? Our location right off of I-295 puts Baltimore just 15 minutes away, and D.C. only 30. You wouldn't want to waste another moment getting home with so much waiting at your doorstep. For the best of all worlds in a Baltimore-area apartment, find your place in Arbors at ArundelPreserve. Call us at 866-421-5258 to learn more.

Description:

The entry level offers access to the 1-car garage and a large family room with walkout to the rear yard. The open main level features a living room, drenched in natural light, spacious dining area, gourmet eat-in kitchen w/ designer tile backsplash, updated appliances & island/breakfast bar and an adjoining family room w/ cozy fireplace & dramatic stone wall. A HUGE master suite has large walk in closet & luxury bath with soaking tub & separate shower. Remaining bedrooms are spacious. Upper level laundry, too! Custom deck overlooks fenced rear yard. Close to Ft. Meade, BWI, major commuter routes and MARC train.
(RLNE3594852) Other Amenities - Other- entry level rec room, walkout, walkout to rear yard, open floorplan, living room, dining area, eat-in kitchen, Garage.

Description:
(703) 825-0957 - Newly Updated 4BR/2BA Townhouse in Severn, MD - Newly updated 4 bedroom 2 bathroom townhome located minutes from Ft. Meade and very convenient to major commuter routes. Features include laminate hardwood flooring throughout a spacious living room and separate dining room with gorgeous crown molding and chair rail details. A galley style kitchen has been fully updated to include newer appliances, tiled floors and a custom tiled backsplash. The 2nd floor has 3 spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet storage space and a fully renovated full bath with tiled floors, custom tiled shower enclosure and new fixtures. There is a finished basement that would make a great 4th bedroom or family room with separate laundry/storage area included. A fully fenced backyard is ideal for entertaining and tenants have access to the community pool located just across the street. Water is included in the rent!
No pets.
Contact JC at (703)825-0957 for details or to schedule an appointment or email jsolorzano@baymgmtgroup.com 
You can apply for this unit or get more information at our website http://www.baymgmtgroup.com/laurel-md-rental-listings/laurel-single-family/
Good Credit Score required. Any slightly lower scores will be considered on a case by case basis.
No Pets Allowed
(RLNE3532177) Other Amenities - Other- laminate hardwood flooring, fully equipped kitchen, basement clubroom, voucher friendly, updated bathroom, Pool, Yard. Appliances - Washer & Dryer. Pet policies - No Dogs Allowed, No Cats Allowed.

Description:
(970) 331-4037 - Wonderful Updated 4BR/3.5BA SFH in Severn, MD - Wonderful Updated 4 Bedroom 3 Full and 1/2 Bathroom brick faced Victorian-style Single Family Home in Severn, MD. Features rich hardwood flooring throughout, a living room, formal dining room, spacious tiled sunroom with cathedral ceilings, laundry area with washer/dryer included, updated  bath and additional family room with gorgeous gas fireplace. Spacious eat in kitchen features tiled flooring, breakfast island, all appliances including dishwasher, and plenty of cabinet storage space. The second floor has an updated hall bath and 4 massive bedrooms including a spacious master suite with walk in closets and full master bath with tiled floors, tiled soaker tub and separate tiled walk in shower. The house has a sprawling basement that has a separate room that would make a great office or 5th bedroom, full bathroom with tiled floors/tiled walk in shower, and a gorgeous clubroom that has tile flooring throughout. There is central air, spacious beautifully landscaped front and backyard with spacious composite deck for entertaining and a 2 car drive way with 2 car attached garage!
Contact David at (970) 331-4037 for details or to schedule an appointment or email djannati@baymgmtgroup.com
Here is the link to apply online:
https://www.baymgmtgroup.com/laurel-md-rental-listings/laurel-single-family/
Good Credit Score required. Any slightly lower scores will be considered on a case by case basis.
No Pets Allowed
(RLNE3508629) Other Amenities - Other- hardwood floors, cathedral ceilings, fireplace, custom tiled floors, kitchen island, fully equipped kitchen, walk in closet, basement clubroom, Garage, Deck. Appliances - Dishwasher, Air Conditioning, Washer & Dryer. Pet policies - No Dogs Allowed, No Cats Allowed.
